---
title: Southern Sweet Mustard Chicken with Roast Potato & Honey-Mustard Veggies
description: A sweet mustard spice mix is just the thing to add plenty of flavour to tender chicken thighs. Add Dijon-spiked roast veggies and a stellar garlic aioli and this easy midweek meal turns into a taste sensation!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ba1d919ae08b57aa923adb2-f5cdbd78.jpg
